<div class="title">Bursts of Alertness</div>
<div class="substance">Caffeine</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Trauma&Exact=1">Trauma</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Trauma. "Bursts of Alertness: An Experience with Caffeine (exp54034)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. May 4, 2011. erowid.org/exp/54034</div>

<br/>



